com.nokia.maps.map

Interface EventListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtendedEventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TouchEventHandler

    public interface EventListener
    This interface provides a callback mechanism for MapComponent interested in user interactions. EventListener is used only if the MapComponent is attached to an active MapDisplay.
